Animated Scene
=== start/en
``Scenes can be used to show a sequence of animated phrases over time.``/en
``Se pueden utilizar escenas para mostrar una secuencia de frases animadas a lo largo del tiempo.``/es
``场景可用于显示随时间变化的一系列动画短语。``/zh
Stage(
    [
        Scene([
            Phrase('The beginning' duration: 3s entering: Pose(scale: 1.1))
            Phrase('The middle' duration: 3s entering: Pose(scale: 1.1))
            Phrase('The end' duration: 3s entering: Pose(scale: 1.1))
	    ])
    ]
)